data.title: Sabert Green Collection
data.meta_description: Features Variety and Versatility: Collection features 60+ high performance, sustainable items consumers are looking for. Temperature Tested: Designed for maximum performance in freezer, microwave, oven*, and heat lamps. Simply Stated: Developed to fit the latest menu trends with a contemporary and clean look. data.text:
Features

Variety and Versatility: Collection features 60+ high performance, sustainable items consumers are looking for.

Temperature Tested: Designed for maximum performance in freezer, microwave, oven*, and heat lamps.

Simply Stated: Developed to fit the latest menu trends with a contemporary and clean look.

Carry Out to Catering: Variety of packaging items available with versatile lids that also fit many container sizes, reducing SKUs.

Confidentaly Compost: Sabert’s unlaminated molded fiber packaging is certified industrial compostable by BPI and Vinçotte and certified home compostable by Vinçotte.**
